WEBVTT

00:00:08.588 --> 00:00:13.468
If I told you not to press 
this big red button,

00:00:14.552 --> 00:00:15.845
what would you do?

00:00:16.345 --> 00:00:19.974
For many people, there’s no greater
motivation to do something

00:00:19.974 --> 00:00:22.101
than being told they can’t.

00:00:22.351 --> 00:00:28.066
So, what is it about being told “no”
that triggers this response?

00:00:29.067 --> 00:00:32.487
One of the most enduring explanations
for this behavior